<br>
some type of root that when used would not allow monster summon.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uqiix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qiix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/20/01 5:10:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> Some spells I'd like to see Druids get at the higher end of the level spectrum...<br>
