<br>
<br>
Group fire and cold buff for 75.<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaani.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maani</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/20/01 8:22:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> would love to see:<br>
<br>
a higher end version of sow, like sow 2 or summit<br>
a insane regen heal, much like celestial elixir / torpor<br>
circle spells for ALL the resits and not just fr + cr<br>
a portal closer to permafrost, running over WK angers me :)<br>
<br>
<br>
probably more if i had more time to think<br>
<br>
tbh druids need some kinda of spell that really only applies to them and no other classes. i mean EVERYTHING we do is done by other classes we really really need something to have to ourselves.<br>
<br>
<br>
maani<br>
55 preserver<br>
guild innit on povar <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaani.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maani</A> at: 7/20/01 8:23:10 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udaktariplainsrunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daktari Plainsrunner</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://home1.gte.net/chiefq/icon1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/20/01 10:16:34 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://home1.gte.net/chiefq/cop.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> Actually staying in class and being realistic:<br>
(I still do not think debuffs and druids mix)<br>
<br>
Wolf form for dungeons, no sow, just atk and ultravision<br>
<br>
Group EB and Group Camo<br>
<br>
Less resisted Snare<br>
<br>
Less resisted nukes, nothing big damage wise<br>
<br>
Faster SoW<br>
<br>
Its a shame I cant go to certain places at 59 and not have a chance in hell of landing a damage spell or snare<br>
<br>
 <p><img src=http://home1.gte.net/chiefq/signamesmall.gif></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udaktariplainsrunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daktari Plainsrunner</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://home1.gte.net/chiefq/icon1.gif BORDER=0> at: 7/20/01 10:17:55 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usymitry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Symitry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/21/01 3:02:34 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> All i'd like to see is a Lure snare i'd be sooo happy <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
-Symitry<br>
58 Preserver <br>
Sphere of Transcendence <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usineras.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sineras</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/22/01 10:52:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> Reincarnate;<br>
Turns target into a randomly generated animal,i.e bear, wolf, skunk, elephant etc..<br>
still need a res but extends res timer.<br>
  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueyeds.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eyeds</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/23/01 5:55:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> Lets face it Druids are in a class of there own(bards are pretty much stuck with us in this, but unlike us they have a definite use at high levels via mana regen).  Unlke other classes who fit into 1 of 3 catagories(Support, magic Damage, Meellee Damage) druids dont really fit into any of the three.  Our Buffs are not needed on a full scale raid.  We cant Heal well enough or fast enough to keep people alive for long.  But our nukes are resisted so much at higher levels that they are not mana efficient to cast. Even our dots do not do enough damage, add to this the fact that a lot of our spells are shared with other classes (regen sow etc) and Wizards monopoly on Lure based DD and translocate spells, we get left in the cold at high end.<br>
<br>
Verent either needs to bring up all our skills (higher DD, heal for more, buff better, Dot better) Or pick one catagory  and make it our main,  Either have us be a support class, or have us be a magic damage class.  Here are my ideas for spells for now Ill think of more later. <br>
<br>
<br>
Indoor Wolf Form: Mana Regen, Atk, Ultravision<br>
Spirit of eagle: Lev, sow (spirit of cheeta speed) Ultravision 1 hour timer (have it break when zoning into a dungeoun if you must)<br>
Lure based Snare (no damage component)<br>
Lure based DD spells at 60 (Fire Ice 850ish damage) or<br>
Lure based DOTs 3K damage over 60 seconds (3 Fire Magic Cold based)<br>
a Heal over time spell 2K heal in say 30 seconds<br>
A real pet (Duel Weilding double attacking teddy bear RAWR!!!!! <p>Eyed <BR>
Visions <BR>
Lanys T'Vyl <BR>
58 Preserver</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urheawindsong.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhea Windsong</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/23/01 11:22:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> Druids are a support class imo. I dunno why people keep saying we arent good enough healers on raids. Due to lack of active raiding clerics in my guild I am often the main and only healer in my groups. I can heal wizards and enchanters the same as a cleric can. Just gimme c2 and I am happy. Thx Chloroblast! Just dont give me any warriors. What we lack in healing power we make up for in versatility.<br>
Even not in a main healer situation, I always find myself useful. Find your niche and be happy with it. <p><p align="center">
