[My Profile]</a></font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uperkynipples.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Perk Ynipples</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/24/01 12:41:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> I'd like to see group versions of Resist Poison and Disease.<br>
Fire (not lure) based snare.<br>
A long lasting fire lure based FR debuffing dot would be nice to... 1000 damage and -60FR over two minutes for 400 mana would be reasonable... but I'm dreaming on this one... the other three are at least feasable =)<br>
<br>
Frankly though, I have a pretty good track record with RFS + shammy and mage Malos...  even on most ToV mobs I can get Breath of Ro to land, and then nukes stick just fine.... Magic based stuff is an entirely different story however.<br>
<br>
Of course if they want to make me really happy, they'll make the epic dot unresistable =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueyeds.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eyeds</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/24/01 1:38:51 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> I would be fine in a support role if I thought we could bring something to it better than someone else but face it we cant.  Shaman can heal better than us at 60 with tupor. Cleric shaman Ench buffs, druids go afk while others use there mana.  <br>
I am really hopeing that Wizard pets from SoL are pure casters with no meellee ability something like lil non stop nukers.  This would increase there damage output without allowing them to take much more damage.<br>
I really think druids need to be moved farther into the damage dealing role.  We dont need to do more damage than wizards or even mages we just need to do it more effieciently than we now can. <p>Eyed <BR>
Visions <BR>
Lanys T'Vyl <BR>
58 Preserver</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urheawindsong.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhea Windsong</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/24/01 5:04:31 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New Spell Ideas</span><hr size=1> I agree with the damage part. Our spells are fine, just too resisted. I think VI is realizing this and is giving us FR debuff spells to try and compenate, but where they really went wrong was upping the magic resistance of these mobs by so much. In effect they made the high end game all about melee's and healers. Would you be ok with having pretty good heals (like we do) and pretty good nukes (which need to be resisted less)?  I think that would be consistent with a druids role pre 50. <p><p align="center">
