<br>
I always thought a new form would be nice.  Form of the Cheetah or Form of the Panther would be nice.  Increased speed, Ultravision, Increased ATK.  <br>
<br>
I also like the idea of a Less Resisted Snare maybe with a longer cast time.  <br>
<br>
